s\n28: \n29: - Treat the current implementation group contract as the primary task input.\n30: - Open the listed source paths and target endpoints before consulting broad phase reports.\n31: - Use full phase reports as indexed references; do not sweep unrelated groups unless this group requires a small shared foundation.\n32: - Update authoritative matrix/capability rows only for this group and any directly required shared surface.\n33: \n34: ## Working Set\n35: \n36: - clusters: _none_\n37: - repair child groups: _none_\n38: - implementation groups: `phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-presentation`\n39: - features: `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-f373ac820e-001-intent-uri-bundle-deeplink-or-cross-scre`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-b4402531cf-006-lifecycle-callback-affecting-screen-init`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-90afaa2416-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-7ad2de0a80-005-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-7fe4304034-003-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`, `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-da76a1d7cc-004-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat`\n40: - capabilities: _none_\n41: - source paths: `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/MainActivity.kt`\n42: - target endpoints: `entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::bootstrapStartRoute`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.isShellAtTop`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj::StartupStore.resolveStartRoute`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.runPrimaryAction`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::primaryActionTarget`, `entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onWindowStageCreate`, `entry/src/main/module.json5::startWindowBackground`, `entry/src/main/module.json5::startWindowIcon`\n43: - acceptance evidence: Closed critical/high features must record sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence.; Build pass alone is not per-feature verification.; Referenced target tests need to be covered by the latest accepted test gate or explicit verificationEvidence.\n44: \n45: ## Current Implementation Groups\n46: \n47: | group | priority | type | title | sources | target domains |\n48: | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n49: | phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-presentation | critical | source-behavior | Source behavior: presentation | app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/MainActivity.kt | app_ability.cj, ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj, ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj |\n50: \n51: ## Plan Contract Alignment\n52: \n53: Plan contract entries are upstream planning evidence. Use them to preserve phase/group ownership, but resolve conflicts through source code and authority JSON records.\n54: - summary: planGroups=2, matchedGroups=2, unmatchedGroups=0\n55: \n56: ### Matched Plan Groups\n57: \n58: | plan group | priority | type | matched groups | source methods | risks | acceptance |\n59: | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n60: | phase-02-startup-session | critical | source-behavior | phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-data-repository, phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-presentation, phase-02-startup-navigation-session-verification-phase-tests-and-evidence | MainActivity.onCreate, SplashViewModel.init, LoginRepositoryImpl.toggleLoginState | Do not replace persistence with in-memory state.; Avoid blocking initialization unless the target framework requires it. | Build gate passes for phase-02-startup-navigation-session.; Target tests prove both login-state values resolve to the correct first route. |\n61: \n62: ## Current Group Contract\n63: \n64: ### `phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-presentation` Source behavior: presentation\n65: \n66: - priority/type: `critical` / `source-behavior`\n67: - source paths: `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/MainActivity.kt`\n68: - feature ids: `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-f373ac820e-001-intent-uri-bundle-deeplink-or-cross-scre`; `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-b4402531cf-006-lifecycle-callback-affecting-screen-init`; `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-90afaa2416-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o`; `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-7ad2de0a80-005-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`; `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-7fe4304034-003-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`; `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-da76a1d7cc-004-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat`\n69: - expected target domains: `app_ability.cj`; `ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj`; `ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj`; `ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj`; `entry/src/main/module.json5`\n70: - required behaviors: `Source review of MainActivity found splash setup and composition startup only; it does not inspect intents, deeplinks, bundles, or cross-screen parameters.`; `MainActivity.onCreate installs splash gating and composes the app only after startup state has chosen the correct start destination.`; `MainActivity hosts the shell by composing `SetupNavigation(startDestination = screen)` once SplashViewModel resolves the startup route.`; `MainActivity observes SplashViewModel state to keep the splash visible while loading and to compose navigation with the re