{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782365639851,"sessionID":"ses_102be2c3dffeRyA4IsDHFUpioX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_r5pL80CunXXl5JENAUTIrqTI","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase02-presentation-mainactivity-row-patch.json\n+{\n+  \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n+  \"purpose\": \"Close the phase-02 MainActivity presentation rows after replacing the bootstrap diagnostic panel with a real startup-seeded route host and shell chrome behavior.\",\n+  \"updates\": [\n+    {\n+      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-90afaa2416-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n+      \"set\": {\n+        \"status\": \"implemented\",\n+        \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n+        \"targetBehavior\": \"EntryAbility still resolves the startup route before content loads, and FoodikeBootstrap now acts as the real phase-02 route host rather than a diagnostic panel. The host is seeded from `bootstrapStartRoute`, keeps onboarding/login/home/history/cart/profile/detail as concrete route surfaces, exposes the shell-owned cart command and home/history tab commands, and limits shell chrome to the same home/history-at-top contract as `SetupNavigation` in the source app.\",\n+        \"verificationEvidence\": [\n+          \"Manual code review: entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate resolves `bootstrapStartRoute` before entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onWindowStageCreate loads the bootstrap page, preserving the source startup-owned shell handoff.\",\n+          \"Manual code review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute, showBottomShell, and runPrimaryAction now compose route-specific surfaces and shell commands instead of a route picker/debug dashboard.\",\n+          \"Test verification: `cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` passed in `D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\Foodike-Harmony\\\\entry` with the phase test env overlay on 2026-06-25, covering entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj including `primaryActionTargetsMatchShellContract`, `bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes`, `resolvesLoggedOutUsersToOnboarding`, and `resolvesLoggedInUsersToHome`.\"\n+        ],\n+        \"targetEndpoints\": [\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::bootstrapStartRoute\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.showBottomShell\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.runPrimaryAction\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::primaryActionTarget\"\n+        ],\n+        \"tests\": [\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.primaryActionTargetsMatchShellContract\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.resolvesLoggedOutUsersToOnboarding\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.resolvesLoggedInUsersToHome\"\n+        ],\n+        \"notes\": \"This row no longer needs `implemented-simplified`: the phase-02 shell remains a single page host, but that still matches the source MainActivity responsibility because the Android activity also only composes the nav host and shell rather than owning feature-page logic directly.\"\n+      }\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-7ad2de0a80-005-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n+      \"set\": {\n+        \"status\": \"implemented\",\n+        \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n+        \"targetBehavior\": \"The startup observable path is now fully represented in the runtime route host: EntryAbility reads the persisted login state, StartupStore resolves the first route before page load, FoodikeBootstrap initializes `currentRoute` from that resolved value, and `@State` updates continue to recompute shell visibility from route changes and shared top-of-list state. This preserves the source MainActivity contract of observing startup state before composing navigation and of keeping shell UI reactive to navigation state.\",\n+        \"verificationEvidence\": [\n+          \"Manual code review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj::StartupStore.resolveStartRoute and entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::EntryAbility.onCreate resolve the startup route before UI content loads, matching the source splash-gated observation contract.\",\n+          \"Manual code review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute and isShellAtTop are `@State` fields that directly drive visible route and shell-chrome recomposition inside the startup host.\",\n+          \"Test verification: `cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` passed in `D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\Foodike-Harmony\\\\entry` with the phase test env overlay on 2026-06-25, covering entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj including `startupStorePublishesResolvedRouteAndClearsLoading`, `resolvesLoggedOutUsersToOnboarding`, `resolvesLoggedInUsersToHome`, and `bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes`.\"\n+        ],\n+        \"targetEndpoints\": [\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj::bootstrapStartRoute\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj::StartupStore.resolveStartRoute\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.isShellAtTop\",\n+          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::showsBottomShell\"\n+        ],\n+        \"tests\": [\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.startupStorePublishesResolvedRouteAndClearsLoading\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.resolvesLoggedOutUsersToOnboarding\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.resolvesLoggedInUsersToHome\",\n+          \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes\"\n+        ],\n+        \"notes\": \"Closed as equivalent because MainActivity only observes one-shot startup state plus nav/shell state for composition; the target now preserves both with runtime store-to-route seeding and `@State`-driven shell updates instead of keeping them in a placeholder bootstrap summary page.\"\n+      }\n+    }\n+  ]\n+}\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA translation-inputs/agent-inputs/phase02-presentation-mainactivity-row-patch.json","metadata":{"diff":"Index: D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase02-presentation-mainactivity-row-patch.json\n===================================================================\n--- D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase02-presentation-mainactivity-row-patch.json\n+++ D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase02-presentation-mainactivity-row-patch.json\n@@ -0,0 +1,61 @