e02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.resolvesLoggedOutUsersToOnboarding\",\n3603:         \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.resolvesLoggedInUsersToHome\",\n3604:         \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes\"\n3605:       ],\n3606:       \"notes\": \"Closed as equivalent because MainActivity only observes one-shot startup state plus nav/shell state for composition; the target now preserves both with runtime store-to-route seeding and `@State`-driven shell updates instead of keeping them in a placeholder bootstrap summary page.\",\n\n(Showing lines 3417-3606 of 9208. Use offset=3607 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-maina-90afaa2416-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n      \"featureName\": \"Navigation surface, menu, drawer, toolbar, or tab command behavior.\",\n      \"sourcePath\": \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/MainActivity.kt\",\n      \"importance\": \"critical\",\n      \"category\": \"kotlin-source\",\n      \"riskTags\": [\n        \"intent_uri\",\n        \"navigation_resource\",\n        \"permissions\",\n        \"screen_lifecycle\",\n        \"state_model\"\n      ],\n      \"keyClasses\": [\n        \"MainActivity\"\n      ],\n      \"keyMethods\": [\n        \"onCreate\"\n      ],\n      \"androidIds\": [],\n      \"dependencies\": [],","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json","time":{"start":1782365656611,"end":1782365656620}},"id":"prt_efd4595ef0019hzvpwsXfdo3gT","sessionID":"ses_102be2c3dffeRyA4IsDHFUpioX","messageID":"msg_efd457d82001b78FsVB1ogBmgu"}}
